{"tid":1162051,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"何猷君戀愛巷塗鴉示愛惹爭議    澳門旅遊局局長︰與文化局商討是否觸法","createTime":"2019-05-19T15:03:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-20T06:08:14.000Z","uid":39464,"like":130,"dislike":30,"uniUserReply":78,"replies":[{"pid":"41ac7846d97909639e963620f8d49ed5a07a2fa0","tid":1162051,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T15:03:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://aamacau.com/files/uploads/2019/05/aamacau-photo-190519_0519_0721.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Faamacau.com%2Ffiles%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F05%2Faamacau-photo-190519_0519_0721.png&h=53d742d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://aamacau.com/files/uploads/2019/05/aamacau-photo-190519_0519_0721-1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Faamacau.com%2Ffiles%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F05%2Faamacau-photo-190519_0519_0721-1.png&h=cdb024a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n賭王何鴻燊四房兒子何猷君早前求婚成功，近日網上廣泛流傳二人在國內明星相親節目《愛的時差》其中一段片段，片中所見何猷君在大三巴下戀愛巷一幅牆壁上塗鴉，向奚夢瑤示愛。而戀愛巷為本澳文物建築，有關片段引起坊間熱議。<br />\n<br />\n旅遊局局長文綺華受訪時稱，事發在世遺城區，有關行為會否抵觸法律，會同文化局等相關部門商討。她稱，拍攝許可一般須向文化局申請，並非旅遊局權限。她亦提醒旅客及市民，胡亂塗鴉可觸犯法律。<br />\n<br />\n至於有關行為會否因「明星效應」向旅客帶出錯誤訊息？文綺華表示，當局與其他部門已計劃了一段時間，針對旅客「一籃子」宣傳控煙、負責任博彩等的重要訊息，正計劃推出小冊子或在官方帳號上宣傳，希望旅客不要將當地習慣帶到澳門，避免因一時興起而誤墮法網。<br />\n<br />\n根據《文化遺產保護法》規定，禁止在被評定或待評定的不動產上刻畫或塗鴉，違反有關規定科處澳門幣2,000至2萬元罰款。<br />\n<br />\n文化局回覆澳門電台查詢時表示，正了解有關節目是否已獲當局發出拍攝許可，將於明日(20日)回覆相關事宜。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://aamacau.com/2019/05/19/%e4%bd%95%e7%8c%b7%e5%90%9b%e6%88%80%e6%84%9b%e5%b7%b7%e5%a1%97%e9%b4%89%e7%a4%ba%e6%84%9b%e6%83%b9%e7%88%ad%e8%ad%b0-%e6%96%87%e7%b6%ba%e8%8f%af%ef%b8%b0%e8%88%87%e6%96%87%e5%8c%96%e5%b1%80%e5%95%86/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faamacau.com%2F2019%2F05%2F19%2F%25e4%25bd%2595%25e7%258c%25b7%25e5%2590%259b%25e6%2588%2580%25e6%2584%259b%25e5%25b7%25b7%25e5%25a1%2597%25e9%25b4%2589%25e7%25a4%25ba%25e6%2584%259b%25e6%2583%25b9%25e7%2588%25ad%25e8%25ad%25b0-%25e6%2596%2587%25e7%25b6%25ba%25e8%258f%25af%25ef%25b8%25b0%25e8%2588%2587%25e6%2596%2587%25e5%258c%2596%25e5%25b1%2580%25e5%2595%2586%2F&d=3iEKCEnQ8TgOeM43nfYZ1%2F5uq9964iqXyfozsjiZLe8%3D&h=83bae750\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://aamacau.com/2019/05/19/%e4%bd%95%e7%8c%b7%e5%90%9b%e6%88%80%e6%84%9b%e5%b7%b7%e5%a1%97%e9%b4%89%e7%a4%ba%e6%84%9b%e6%83%b9%e7%88%ad%e8%ad%b0-%e6%96%87%e7%b6%ba%e8%8f%af%ef%b8%b0%e8%88%87%e6%96%87%e5%8c%96%e5%b1%80%e5%95%86/</a>"},{"pid":"c6d324bb9b61025006b4ca156a3b8b0c712ee8fa","tid":1162051,"uid":84212,"like":515,"dislike":4,"score":511,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T15:05:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5ead24b0efb17ab92a5312f18049d9302ecee6be","tid":1162051,"uid":71508,"like":106,"dislike":3,"score":103,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T15:05:44.000Z","msg":"拉佢坐監啦"},{"pid":"d94abb62e3759ce9df7638ac742f5c54d3de05eb","tid":1162051,"uid":235152,"like":296,"dislike":2,"score":294,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T15:07:40.000Z","msg":"去得大陸多連寫大字都學埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee915cc54ae766c03480d9c9048a66bb4a26bd21","tid":1162051,"uid":35598,"like":146,"dislike":2,"score":144,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T15:08:40.000Z","msg":"修復古蹟唔撚使錢咩<br />\n一於抄佢家啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"752c985c58f1a0214839b6e3f59f42bc47c1d4cf","tid":1162051,"uid":117679,"like":278,"dislike":0,"score":278,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T15:09:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />點解咁撚on9？<br />\n<br />\n四姨太快啲接佢返屋企先啦⋯"},{"pid":"b69a440bb5a66166e9f5b779a3bc2104867bf625","tid":1162051,"uid":13653,"like":55,"dislike":0,"score":55,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T15:10:10.000Z","msg":"小明到此一遊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65031f281ffedd2a629ddf52e8c3908780f3c13e","tid":1162051,"uid":76747,"like":50,"dislike":1,"score":49,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T15:10:48.000Z","msg":"無所謂啦,<br />\n佢比錢買起塊牆有幾